#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn32.56"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn32.56:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 32 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 32 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn32.56:0.2"
msgid "1. Valāhakavagga "
msgstr "1. Gods of the Clouds "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn32.56:0.3"
msgid "56. Vātavalāhakasutta "
msgstr "56. Gods of the Windy Clouds "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli3.257, sc1
msgctxt "sn32.56:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ. "
msgstr "At Sāvatthī. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn32.56:1.2"
msgid "Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho so bhikkhu bhagavantaṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "Seated to one side, that mendicant said to the Buddha: "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn32.56:1.3"
msgid "“ko nu kho, bhante, hetu, ko paccayo, yenekadā vāto hotī”ti? "
msgstr "“Sir, what is the cause, what is the reason why sometimes it becomes windy?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn32.56:1.4"
msgid "“Santi, bhikkhu, vātavalāhakā nāma devā. "
msgstr "“Mendicant, there are what are called gods of the windy clouds. "

msgctxt "sn32.56:1.5"
msgid "Tesaṃ yadā evaṃ hoti: "
msgstr "Sometimes they think: "

msgctxt "sn32.56:1.6"
msgid "‘yannūna mayaṃ sakāya ratiyā vaseyyāmā’ti, tesaṃ taṃ cetopaṇidhimanvāya vāto hoti. "
msgstr "‘Why don’t we revel in our own kind of enjoyment?’ Then, in accordance with their wish, it becomes windy. "

msgctxt "sn32.56:1.7"
msgid "Ayaṃ kho, bhikkhu, hetu, ayaṃ paccayo, yenekadā vāto hotī”ti. "
msgstr "This is the cause, this is the reason why sometimes it becomes windy.” "

msgctxt "sn32.56:1.8"
msgid "Chappaññāsamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
